@startuml
title Subscription Workflow - State
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Disabled
Disabled --> Enabled : init config(enabled=true)
Enabled --> Candidate : symbol enters target set
Candidate --> Subscribed : subscribe(symbol)
Subscribed --> Protected : still in target set
Protected --> Stale : removed from target set
Stale --> Subscribed : symbol reappears
Stale --> Unsubscribed : TTL elapsed + unsubscribe(symbol)
Unsubscribed --> Candidate : symbol returns
Enabled --> TempTracked : signal-driven temporary symbol
TempTracked --> Candidate : included in runtime context
TempTracked --> Expired : TTL elapsed
Expired --> [*]
@enduml
